<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Account Activation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Xplora</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <%= user.name %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for registering with Xplora. To complete the activation process and start using our platform, please use the following activation code:</p>
      <h2><%= activationCode %></h2>
      <p>Please enter the activation code within the next 5 minutes.</p>
      <p>Once your account is activated, you'll have access to a wide range of destinations, tours, and resources to enhance your travel experiences.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please feel free to contact our support team at:</p>
      <p><a href="mailto:support@xplora.com">support@xplora.com</a></p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>Xplora Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you did not register for an Xplora account, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
